---
import Base from '../../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE, t } from '../../../../data/i18n.js';
const lang = 'it';
---
<Base lang={lang} title="Visita Guidata a Segovia — Prenota con María Victoria Solaz" description="Visita guidata a Segovia. Acquedotto, Alcázar, Cattedrale. Guida interprete diplomata." path="/segovia/visita-guidata/">
  <div class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/img/segovia/acueducto-noche.webp" alt="Aqueduct of Segovia" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="1600" height="1097" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Visita Guidata</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-sepia mb-8">Segovia — Patrimonio dell’Umanità UNESCO</p>
    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Durata</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Da concordare</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Prezzo</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">Su richiesta</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70">Lingue</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">IT · ES · EN · FR · PT</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Un percorso teatralizzato dall’Acquedotto romano all’Alcázar dove Isabella fu proclamata regina, passando per la Cattedrale gotica e la Zecca Reale di Filippo II.</p>
        <p>Per chi vuole capire Segovia oltre il cochinillo. Si combina con El Escorial e Ávila.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="cta-green rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Prenota la tua visita</h2>
      <p class="text-sepia mb-4">Contatta direttamente María Victoria</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/34659953930?text=Ciao%20María%20Victoria%2C%20vorrei%20una%20visita%20guidata%20a%20Segovia" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block btn-whatsapp px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-sepia/70 mt-4">Risposta abituale entro 24 ore</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
